HEADWORD: Roach-backed
<hw>Roach"-backed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a back
like that of roach; -- said of a horse whose back a convex instead of a
concave curve.</def>⟦br⟧
